# Critical Mistakes

> **Purpose:** Learn from corrections. Never repeat the same mistake twice.

## When to Add

- ✅ User corrected you ("No, don't do it that way...")
- ✅ User expressed frustration ("I already told you...")
- ✅ You realized you misunderstood something important
- ✅ You broke something and had to undo it
- ✅ You went down a wrong path for 10+ minutes

## Format

```markdown
### YYYY-MM-DD: [Short title]

**Mistake:** [What you did wrong]
**Correction:** [What you should do instead]
**Why it matters:** [Impact / why user cares]
```

